            <div class="jumbotron">
                <h2>
                    Hello, World!
                </h2>
                <p>
                    This is a site made to demonstrate the core principles of MVX using ASP.NET 5 with Razor pages. Contains
                    two pages, one for keeping track of inventory and one for budgeting. I titled it RVLife designating it could 
                    be useful for keeping track of purchased RV items and the monthly budget. Not a complex site but demonstrates 
                    the core foundation to making web applications.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
