    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2>
                Inventory
            </h2>
            <p>
                We like to keep track of all our items. This helps us keep up with our spending and making sure we have what we need.
                It also keeps track of where we got something at and what we paid. We can store notes like specific model details or
                warranty information we want to keep handy.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn" asp-controller="Item">View inventory »</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2>
                Budgeting
            </h2>
            <p>
                If you are not budgeting, then life is costing you too much. With so many things we want to do, being careful on what our
                monthly expenses are is not an option. This is our simple way of keeping track of our routine monthly expenses so we 
                understand where we are at.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn" asp-controller="Expense">View budget »</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2>
                Sample third column
            </h2>
            <p>
                We like to keep track of all our items. This helps us keep up with our spending and making sure we have what we need.
